Sigil Stone Alternative

Welcome to my Sigil Stone Alternative for The Elder Scrolls IV: Oblivion.

What this plug-in does is a complete Overhaul to the Sigil Stones. From looking at the Sigil Stones in the CS, I found there are a few things that I felt was wrong with them.
http://www.uesp.net/wiki/Oblivion:Sigil_Stones going here you will see the Default settings for them. You will see that they are unbalanced being there is a few that there lower level counterparts are more powerful then the best of the best and a few of the level 17+ stones being weak compared to others. 

Sigil Stone Ranks
Level   Type
1-4      Descendent
5-8      Subjacent
9-12     Latent
13-16    Ascendent
17+      Transcendent


What I have done was take all of the Sigil Stones and redone them the way I think the stones should be done. I tried to make them based off the quest that these Stones are suppose to be powerful relics that power the gate to functions should be better then what you can make at a Enchanters Alter. 

